Terminals unused in grammar

    BREAK
    CONTINUE
    DO
    K_NULL
    WHEN
    OP_ERROR
    ILL_IDENT
    UNCLOSED_COMMENT
    COULD_NOT_MATCH
    KEYWORD_ERROR
    NEG
